<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4747196>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 23. Radulopora radula (Marsson); Late Cretaceous, early Maastrichtian, Lundegårde, Nordjylland, Denmark. (a,b) SMF 29628; (a) branch fragment; (b) autozooids with closure plates and impressions of opercular sclerites (arrowed). (c,f) SMF 29629; (c) branch bifurcation, including a zooid (arrowed) with partial closure plate; (f) avicularium; (d,e) SMF 29630; (d) autozooids and avicularia; (e) fertile autozooid. Scale bars: a = 1 mm; b, d, e = 200 µm; c = 500 µm; f = 100 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4747196/files/figure.png" .

